se hearing amplifiers or a microphone and \nheadphones as an alternative to hearing aids. Ensure the hearing appliance is operational. \n\n\u2022 \n\nInterview the patient and ask about hearing function in different situations (e.g., hearing staff or family \nmembers, talking to visitors, using telephone, watching TV, participation in group discussion).", "type": "Document"}}